11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 10 O.S. 2021, Section 405.4, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 405.4. A. Any person with a bachelor's degree or
15 postgraduate degree shall be considered as having met the
16 educational requirements for a director of a full-time child care
17 center required by the Department of Human Services. Nothing in
18 this section shall be construed as to affect annual continuing
19 education requirements. The director of a child care center may
20 also qualify as a master teacher for children of all ages.
21 B. 1. Any person replacing a master teacher at a child care
22 center shall be granted a one-year probationary period to fulfill
23 the educational qualifications required by the Department for a
24 master teacher. The Department may extend the probationary period
