5 C. Licensed child care facilities opened or expanded before
6 November 1, 2016, shall have thirty-five (35) square feet of floor
7 area per infant in rooms occupied only by infants. New construction
8 and existing space not previously licensed for child care after
9 November 1, 2016, shall have forty (40) square feet of floor area
10 per infant in rooms occupied only by infants.
11 D. In determining the number of master teachers required based
12 on license capacity and desired Star level, after school care
13 children shall not be counted toward the license capacity.
14 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
